en.Intro:
[GraphGen](https://github.com/open-sciencelab/GraphGen) is a tool for generating synthetic SFT training data. 

 By uploading your text chunks (such as knowledge in agriculture, healthcare, or marine science) and filling in the LLM API key, you can generate the training data required by **LLaMA-Factory** and **xtuner** online. After the synthesis is complete, we will automatically delete user information.

zh.Intro:
[GraphGen](https://github.com/open-sciencelab/GraphGen) 是一个合成 SFT 训练数据的工具。

 上传你的文本块（如农业、医疗、海洋知识），填写 LLM api key，即可在线生成 **LLaMA-Factory**、**xtuner** 所需训练数据。结束后我们将自动删除用户信息。
